  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1019">
<l>kulañcuṭuṅ koḷkai piḻaippi ṉalañcuṭu </l>
<l>nāṇiṉmai niṉṟak kaṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Want of manners injures one's family; but want of modesty injures one's character.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
